title: Remember WENN Ep 07 - 10
description:
Remember WENN.  Originally created for and broadcast on AMC.


The below was AMC website (back when you could find anything about this show there):

Will AMC be re-broadcasting or airing new episodes of "Remember WENN"?  There are no plans to re-broadcast or produce additional episodes of "Remember WENN," nor is it available for purchase.

AMC has continued to state that WENN is not licensed for sale and will not
be licensed for sale. I am strongly opposed to pirates profiting from
others&#039; work; it should be shared among fans freely if we cannot obtain it
in a way that would support the artists.

I do very strongly support actually paying the creators, of course. I&#039;ve
spent too much time in green rooms with starving artists to think
otherwise. :-) The day I learn that AMC has licensed WENN for legal
purchase, these torrents will be disabled and I will purchase a full set of
high-quality DVDs as soon as they are available.
